OL,3,CIrish justice minister 'will consider'
OL,4,Cinquiry into Creeslough explosion
OL,6,FIreland's justice minister is to
OL,7,Fconsider holding an inquiry into the
OL,8,FCreeslough explosion in which 10
OL,9,Fpeople died, the families of the
OL,10,Fvictims have said.
OL,12,FAn investigation into the explosion is
OL,13,F"key" to ending the suffering of the
OL,14,Ffamilies of the victims, a lawyer
OL,15,Facting on their behalf said.
OL,17,FThey also have called on the justice
OL,18,Fminister to travel to Co Donegal to
OL,19,Fmeet families and survivors.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@EO]
