OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775848268
OL,3,CIrish justice minister 'will consider'
OL,4,Cinquiry into Creeslough explosion
OL,6,FFour men, three women and three
OL,7,Fchildren, aged between five and 59,
OL,8,Fdied in the explosion at a building
OL,9,Fcomplex in the Co Donegal village on
OL,10,FOctober 7 2022.
OL,12,FThe 10 victims were: Robert Garwe and
OL,13,Fhis five-year-old daughter Shauna
OL,14,FFlanagan-Garwe, Catherine O'Donnell
OL,15,Fand her 13-year-old son James
OL,16,FMonaghan, fashion student Jessica
OL,17,FGallagher, Celtic fan Martin McGill,
OL,18,FJames O'Flaherty from Sydney,
OL,19,FAustralia, shop worker Martina Martin,
OL,20,Fcarpenter Hugh "Hughie" Kelly and 14-
OL,21,Fyear-old Leona Harper.
OL,26,@|D@POU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
