OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775848268
OL,3,CIrish justice minister 'will consider'
OL,4,Cinquiry into Creeslough explosion
OL,6,F"My wee girl was killed on 7
OL,7,F(October), and she was 14 when she was
OL,8,Fkilled. January past she should have
OL,9,Fbeen 18, and she should have been
OL,10,Fmaking her prom and so on. And you've
OL,11,Fgot all them milestones in front of
OL,12,Fyou, and we would really, really love
OL,13,Fto see if he could agree to giving us
OL,14,Fthe inquiry right now."
